---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import SplitPane from '../components/SplitPane.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="About — Finn Stäblein" description="About Finn Stäblein.">
  <SplitPane>
    <div slot="left" class="about-text">
      <h2 class="section-label label">This site</h2>

      <p>
        Hey, I'm Finn. This is a place where I keep notes on things I'm reading, watching, and working on.
      </p>

      <p>
        It's a living document - a place to think in public and keep track of what's shaped my perspective.
      </p>

      <h2 class="section-label label">About me</h2>

      <p>
        I grew up in the scenic landscape of Southern Germany with a love for sports, science, and the outdoors. I started rowing when I was 10, and the sport shaped my life immensely for the next 8 years. It taught me the value of discipline, perseverance, and shaping a purpose. At the age of 18, I realized a dream by representing Germany as part of the national rowing team, winning gold at the Junior World Championships in the Men's Double.
      </p>

      <p>
        Driven by the same desire of creating a purpose, I developed an interest in entrepreneurship. So, at 18, I moved to Berlin to join Europe's fastest-growing startup at the time.
      </p>

      <p>
        I graduated from Stanford in June 2026, where I majored in Computational Biology.
      </p>

      <p>
        Now, I've joined <a href="https://www.floodgate.com/" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Floodgate</a> as Mike Maple's Chief of Staff. I wouldn't have gone into Venture for many other roles bc I didn't want to spend my time networking and throwing around with LP money just to give them a worse return than they could get by just putting their money in the S&P 500.
      </p>

      <p>
        My predecessor, Sam wrote an <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7474870123758129152/" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">essay</a> about what it's like working with Mike; which gives you a glimpse of why I'm doing exactly that now.
      </p>

      <p class="about-contact">
        Feel free to reach out via
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/finn-staeblein" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>,
        <a href="mailto:finn@floodgate.com" class="contact-link">email</a>,
        or join me for a run or bike ride around the Bay!
      </p>
    </div>

    <div slot="right" class="about-images">
      <img
        src="/images/about/rowing-single.jpg"
        alt="Finn rowing a single scull below a hilltop fortress in Germany"
        class="about-photo fade-in pos-left"
        width="1600"
        height="1199"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <img
        src="/images/about/rowing-worlds-2021.jpg"
        alt="Finn on the podium at the 2021 World Rowing Junior Championships"
        class="about-photo fade-in pos-right"
        width="1000"
        height="750"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <img
        src="/images/about/stanford-bike.jpg"
        alt="Finn with his bike in Stanford's Main Quad"
        class="about-photo fade-in pos-center"
        width="1200"
        height="1600"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <img
        src="/images/about/skiing.jpg"
        alt="Finn skiing with his dad in the mountains"
        class="about-photo fade-in pos-left"
        width="1200"
        height="1600"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <img
        src="/images/about/whitney-summit.jpg"
        alt="Finn at a mountain summit while hiking"
        class="about-photo fade-in pos-right"
        width="1200"
        height="1600"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <img
        src="/images/about/graduation-parents.jpg"
        alt="Finn with his parents at Stanford graduation"
        class="about-photo fade-in pos-center"
        width="1200"
        height="1600"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <img
        src="/images/about/graduation-portrait.jpg"
        alt="Finn at his Stanford graduation"
        class="about-photo fade-in pos-left"
        width="1055"
        height="1600"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
  </SplitPane>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .about-text {
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  .section-label {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    margin-top: var(--space-12);
  }

  .section-label:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .about-contact {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
  }

  .contact-link {
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
    transition: color var(--duration-fast) ease;
  }

  .contact-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .about-images {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  .about-photo {
    display: block;
    width: 50%;
    height: auto;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  /* Staggered alignment down the column */
  .about-photo.pos-left {
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .about-photo.pos-center {
    align-self: center;
  }

  .about-photo.pos-right {
    align-self: flex-end;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-photo {
      width: 65%;
    }
  }
</style>
